For the first time in Vietnam, you will have the opportunity to taste, enjoy and explore around 400 wines from 8 countries including France, Chile, Italy, Argentina, Australia, New Zealand, America and South Africa in the presence of 23 wineries representatives.
To celebrate the significant 20th Anniversary of Da Loc company, we will be very delighted to have the hounour of your presence at our upcoming Da Loc’s Wine Festival event in Ha Noi and Ho Chi Minh City.
We will indulge you in a real world of wine culture
